58
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:50,240
What does that mean? For plus duration: for 
ten years, four eight months, for five hours.  

59
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:58,240
Since plus starting point. When did 
something start? From when? since 2011,  

60
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:05,840
since March. Those are my starting 
points. I've lived here for 10 years.  

61
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:14,320
I've had a bad shoulder since summer. For and 
Since are really common with the present perfect  

62
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:20,640
because they show us that something is 
continuing up to now. I still live here.  

63
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:27,920
