But! I've met thousands of students since I 
started teaching. I've met - present perfect.  

67
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:11,120
I'm still teaching now, great. Since I 
started? What? Since plus past simple?  

68
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:21,600
In this sentence here, Since plus I started, is 
my starting point. I'm not saying my starting  

69
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:28,000
is continuing up to the present. Let me give you 
the same sentence, but I'll change things around  

70
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:37,280
