86
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:34,800
We're out of coffee pods. Don't 
worry, I've already ordered some.

87
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:43,840
Because of my sprained ankle, now I can't go 
on that skiing trip. Because of the bad news,  

