93
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:26,960
Both tenses have different grammatical 
structures. Verb 2 for past simple.  

94
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:31,040
Have/Has plus verb three, past 
participle - for the present perfect  

95
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:38,880
It's all about something that is finished 
or unfinished - time. Finished: I drank three  

96
00:12:38,880 --> 00:12:44,880
