I've drunk three cups of coffee today.  

97
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:55,040
Life experiences. Finished: My grandma went to over 
50 countries. Unfortunately, she's not alive now.  

98
00:12:56,880 --> 00:13:04,400
Unfinished: She's been to over 50 
countries. She's still alive. Actions.  

99
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:13,680
Finished: I lived there for 20 years. Unfinished: 
I have lived here for 20 years. Connection to  

100
